For making hot chocolate you need:
1)milk (1 cup if 1 serving)
2)cocoa powder (2 tablespoon per serving)
3)sugar or rock sugar (as per sweetness needed)
4)chocolate(optional)

Now the steps:

first of all add milk to a bowl and boil it until it is warm enough
now add the cocoa powder little by little so that it does not form lumps
now mix it and add sugar along with chocolate and mix until sugar and
chocolate melts 

now you can serve yourself the hot chocolate
(you can add cinnamon powder on top to get a healty treat)
